      <title>塔利班法律进一步限制妇女权利引发全球抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/taliban-laws-further-curbing-women-s-rights-bring-global-outcry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿富汗塔利班政府出台的新法律引发了全球的谴责，包括禁止妇女在公共场合讲话或露面，并可能危及该政权争取合法性的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/taliban-laws-further-curbing-women-s-rights-bring-global-outcry</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 15:22:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
